Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的自我牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.60,0:01:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不过是自我满足
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.70,0:01:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得这样就能救得了谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.25,0:01:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只是想保护自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.38,0:01:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丝毫不懂活下来的人的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说这么天真的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是把痛苦推给了别人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍视你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.29,0:01:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:01:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们代替你背负着这份痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.78,0:02:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不想失去不顾自己死活的你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.29,0:02:02.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才说了一半
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.50,0:02:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去你谁都保护不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无视自己生命的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没资格保护别人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.01,0:02:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别总一副悲剧主人公的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.95,0:02:16.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}烦死了…烦死了…烦死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.14,0:02:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤害自己又伤害别人 你打算这么活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.44,0:02:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.96,0:02:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H666666&\b0\pos(319,372)\blur5}泪之池
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明没有力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却是个靠自我满足就想拯救别人的怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又有什么不对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.99,0:02:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然闯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后自说自话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底了解我什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…明明什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被否定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脏死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不被期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以至少…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要给周围带来麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受伤的只有我一个人就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难过也好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.02,0:03:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悲伤也好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要这样想着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将来就算所有人都离开我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我死了 也不会有人受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只不过是自作多情!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从未想过自己能和别人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:03:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说 总算是稍微了解你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能放心前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 差不多该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底说了些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些话 我对基尔都没说过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:30.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎轻松了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到学生会带着枪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是负责护卫的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈特雷伊家的侍从吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 洛蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是擦伤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.00,0:04:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很头疼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是奈特雷伊也介入的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么做才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是很简单吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不杀掉就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾达
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸色好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狮子?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是灵体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追～到～了～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请叫它「里昂」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰克想和我们谈谈了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.11,0:05:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真难缠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:06:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是灵体的话 要赢就很难了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.37,0:06:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算叫他们逃跑 似乎也不会听话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也只能拼死一搏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 会用剑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防身的方法还算是被逼着学了一些的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止 都觉得逃避比较轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许比你还用得好一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 里昂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来和小猫们一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾略特!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 好弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我没有实战经验嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里昂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:06:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能杀了他们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要一点一点折磨他们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再引出杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰克?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 杰克说过的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有这个资格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.39,0:07:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 告诉我!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用染血黑兔力量的方法!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让艾达和这家伙死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我 杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然并非明白一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果因为我的努力 别人能避免受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就来承受那些人的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 要连自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起保护
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也赞成这种想法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要专心救援同伴就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…你有那个资格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里昂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,染血黑兔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 终于出来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「沙布利耶之悲剧」的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰克·贝萨流士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.09,0:09:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八音盒的音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会是什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格连大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可真是 多么英姿飒爽的女士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然看上去很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过不是什么了不起的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才不是应该说自己不可疑的么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.01,0:10:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自称不可疑的家伙的话 只会更让人怀疑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再戏弄夏洛特了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么爱称就叫洛蒂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面 洛蒂小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是 杰克·贝萨流士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是个不出名的音乐盒工匠罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰克·贝萨流士…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝萨流士家族是个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有了不起财产的三流贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是家族的第三个儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是父母没对他有任何期望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他太过自由随性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.53,0:11:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个以自我为中心的让人恼火的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个巴司卡瓦的府邸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般人可是进不来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看我这样 怎么着也算是贵族吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你每天都是怎么混进来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人告诉我秘密通道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密通道?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「想来的时候用这个就好了」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.33,0:11:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格连说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像总是来见格连大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…你和格连大人是…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么关系!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:12:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种问题 直接去问格连就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…当然不可能的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是个容易搭话的人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格连大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你说了多少我们的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴司卡瓦家族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其存在一直在黑暗中隐藏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其职责也和一般贵族完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 管理这个家族的唯一当家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格连·巴司卡瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我又不在乎他那种沉重的称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙对我来说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是能相互竞争的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 总而言之 是朋友啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是非常没有实感的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所知道的格连大人喜欢一个人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不喜欢像他那种烦人的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:12:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的得意之作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你做的?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你不是八音盒工匠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是八音盒还是怀表
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动力源是一样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.92,0:13:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有好好做完自己的工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…这个曲子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时也听到过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优美的旋律呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.81,0:13:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么曲子?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫蕾西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.07,0:13:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那曲子是我作的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格连大人…笑了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是格连大人和杰克共同创造出来的艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没有加入他们 让我多少有些不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.83,0:14:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了格连大人的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为那样就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只是一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望这样平静的时光能继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.97,0:14:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格连大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才你说了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王公贵族聚集的这座沙布利耶 为何要这么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格连大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.48,0:14:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管女人还是孩子 都没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城里的人一个不留都杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连巴司卡瓦的红色斗篷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都染成了黑色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不断屠杀 屠杀 屠杀…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样 这就被称作「沙布利耶之悲剧」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴司卡瓦的子民
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会在这种情况下再会呢 洛蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格连大人现在到底在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛蒂 别搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在此现身可不是为了聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了将你们击退
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 一副了不起的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被称为英雄你很得意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:15:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明还说是挚友!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那件事情之后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.72,0:16:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的贝萨流士家族可是出名了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为了出名才杀了格连的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 洛蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最后一次的警告了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在染血黑兔的力量面前 你们是赢不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.27,0:16:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛蒂 我不能说太多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了保护最重要的朋友的名誉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.71,0:16:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们让相同的悲剧重演的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.97,0:16:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将再度化身死神的利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是遵从主人的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你想杀死格连大人多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管多少次我都会再次找到给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类还真是软弱的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.82,0:17:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是我 还是格连…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么东西进入大脑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你要这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.61,0:17:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我 格连!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰克…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想杀了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.85,0:18:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才闯进我内心的是…杰克的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想杀了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这般发自内心的狂吼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却对朋友拔出了剑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:18:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么悲伤痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:19:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸口仿佛要裂开一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的话 一定会逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不向朋友拔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果 就算是要被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.73,0:19:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会接受那样的现实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样就能救谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没那么想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.61,0:19:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像他所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是不想伤害自己罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类是多么软弱的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说那种话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都算软弱的话 我又算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都不能承受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 我连自己都无法面对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是逃避自我的报应
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕被拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却对周围极度敏感的胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:20:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定在为那个小孩 感受到的寒冷而悲伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人指出就不能察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底身处何方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连被这么问的意义也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我比任何人 任何东西 都不了解自己!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.56,0:20:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是有点泄气 别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说为什么用敬语
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于意识到了自己的无能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.98,0:20:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾略特说过头了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不顾别人的感受自说自话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的坏毛病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…一直都在同一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.38,0:20:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那时起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再没能前进一步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.76,0:20:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太没出息了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.96,0:21:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如里奥所说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,0:21:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一点也不了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你也注意到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.61,0:21:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻你已经朝前迈出一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后的事随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要继续前进 还是回头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是走另一条路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.59,0:21:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全由你自己决定!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.11,0:21:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真温柔呢 艾略特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.25,0:21:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉察到…觉察到自己的软弱的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那就是变强的开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.07,0:21:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还能向前吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.11,0:21:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怀抱着凌乱的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.73,0:22:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不让这片光明蒙羞…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.07,0:23:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}不过是接吻 我和奥兹也做过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.02,0:23:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}世间一般把那称为酒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.12,0:23:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}进入少女状态了……!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.42,0:23:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}多少注意下气氛啊 基尔!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.56,0:23:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}大姐姐会温柔地教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.43,0:24:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}浪漫是啥? 好吃吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.26,0:24:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}我……我必须按自己的方式前进
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.90,0:24:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&}下回 流逝之声